This is my vim config. To use it:

- Clone this:
    ```sh
    cd ~/.vim
    git clone git@github.com:idanarye/vimConfig.git
    ```

- Clone vim-plug:
    ```sh
    cd ~/.vim
    git clone https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug.git
    ```

Add these lines to your .vimrc:
    ```vim
    let $MYVIMRC="$VIM/vimfiles/bundle/_vimrc"
    source $MYVIMRC

    set runtimepath+=/home/idanarye/.vim/vim-plug/
    runtime plug.vim

    call plug#begin('~/.vim/plugins')
    source ~/.vim/vimConfig/plugins.vim
    call plug#end()
```
